@startuml Amdox-ERP-State
title Amdox ERP — State Diagram (Invoice Lifecycle)

[*] --> DRAFT : create invoice

DRAFT --> PENDING : submit
DRAFT --> CANCELLED : discard

PENDING --> APPROVED : manager approves
PENDING --> DRAFT : request changes
PENDING --> CANCELLED : reject

APPROVED --> PARTIALLY_PAID : partial payment
APPROVED --> PAID : full payment
APPROVED --> OVERDUE : due date passed

PARTIALLY_PAID --> PAID : remaining paid
PARTIALLY_PAID --> OVERDUE : due date passed

OVERDUE --> PAID : payment received

PAID --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of APPROVED
  3-way match:
  PO + GRN + Invoice
end note
@enduml
